QuestData.Title: Back to The Heart
QuestData.Description:
We should hurry back to Ardenweald!
You go on ahead and find Ysera. I'll escort the Stonewright there and make sure Huln gets back.
QuestData.LogDescription: Return to Ysera in front of the Heart of the Forest in Ardenweald.
